Description: Finite candidate-set approximate optimal designs for group testing
    and related experiments, using convex optimization (CVXR) and equivalence
    checks. Implements the information matrix and cost structure for the
    prevalence / sensitivity / specificity model used in Huang et al. (2020), as
    in Yeh, Wong, and Zhou (arXiv:2508.08445).
URL: https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.08445
